{"tid":2142721,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"人行：利率過低或導致「資源錯配」及「脫實向虛」","createTime":"2020-08-06T15:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T17:48:48.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8921fd51727da464246c2d98f9f040a8812bea49","tid":2142721,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T15:04:39.000Z","msg":"人行：利率過低或導致「資源錯配」及「脫實向虛」<br />\n2020-08-06 HKT 22:09<br />\n<br />\n&quot;人行發布第2季度貨幣政策執行報告，指出部分發達經濟體實施零利率甚至負利率政策，但政策效果不及預期.......認為利率過低會導致「資源錯配」及「脫實向虛」等負面影響。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;人行指出，今年以來堅持實施正常貨幣政策，保持利率水平與中國發展階段及經濟形勢動態配合，本外幣利差處於合適區間，人民幣資產吸引力上升。 &quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542267-20200806.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542267-20200806.htm&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=c425a78b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542267-20200806.htm&h=4b185bca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542267-20200806.htm</a>"},{"pid":"04c573800f98993f2e17cfb64fe1691ee6705f46","tid":2142721,"uid":60338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:30:34.000Z","msg":"咁你咪加息囉。屌你"},{"pid":"8d95cbf187b34d2898c2ddf7d8e7ad150b7e16a1","tid":2142721,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T17:14:21.000Z","msg":"教緊美國佬"},{"pid":"5cb7d3f4575978465fac5ac7fc3fd64df111875c","tid":2142721,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T17:48:48.000Z","msg":"慳的啦人行，以你地支那人既特性，乜鳩實業都可以俾你搞到虛鳩晒，咁投資係邊度有閪分別咩，正宗世界毒瘤。"}]}